-result=\"on\">定義一個架構，該架構允許 NgModule 包含以下內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Defines a schema that allows an NgModule to contain the following:</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SchemaMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">SchemaMetadata</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用（<code>-</code>）命名法的非 Angular 元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Non-Angular elements named with dash case (<code>-</code>).</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以破折號（<code>-</code>）命名的元素屬性。破折號是自訂元素的命名約定。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Element properties named with dash case (<code>-</code>).\nDash case is the naming convention for custom elements.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - errors/NG8001\n - guide/testing-attribute-directives\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA#custom_elements_schema\n - api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA#description\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L45-L46\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L45-L46\n-->"}